miSg_HgQS469Am8BodHZ0tT-Rg&oe=66FFEAE2"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "1934382610375855", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974473_1934382613709188_7156337812617042679_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=908mnFqey4gQ7kNvgGfMaYC&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCKy8DFPO0qCwosqZS5dx_b30U8lQjCN4r4pcCwi4rrGA&oe=66FFD4F3"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "1524760081483769", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974531_1524760084817102_6497712644828891067_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rMKcS9gBMOkQ7kNvgGa1nw1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA1RiDrnFv0rePoSGZBnqdwM9K0AeiHKCh7BYB4mSy_vQ&oe=66FFD3EF"}, "display_name": "Mystery Box VR: Hidden Secrets", "keywords": [], "long_description": " AN IMMERSIVE VR PUZZLE EXPERIENCE\nInteract with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.\n\nYou won't be able to compare reality with fiction.\n\n# DISCOVER INVENTIONS\nOnce you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.\n\nIt's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!\n\n# IMMERSIVE SOUNDTRACK\nPlay the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.\n\n# HINTS\nGot stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)\n\n# MULTILANGUAGE\nAvailable in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.\n\nThe game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device", "short_description": "A VR escape room game where you have to solve intriguing riddles to open boxes and discover nice stories about popular inventions!"}, 